little, tiny domains for just

01:03:50.240 --> 01:03:53.260 align:middle line:84%
really maybe several
thousand dollars.

01:03:53.260 --> 01:03:55.610 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people look at
it, and their heart opens.

01:03:55.610 --> 01:03:58.800 align:middle line:90%
It's like, that's so appealing.

01:03:58.800 --> 01:04:00.225 align:middle line:90%
Talk about that for just a sec.

01:04:00.225 --> 01:04:02.100 align:middle line:84%
ZEUS: I think-- and I
do want to leave people

01:04:02.100 --> 01:04:03.410 align:middle line:90%
with a very hopeful note.

01:04:03.410 --> 01:04:05.670 align:middle line:84%
I am a very hopeful
person in this.

01:04:05.670 --> 01:04:08.576 align:middle line:84%
Even as the system collapses,
I don't see that as a tragedy.

01:04:08.576 --> 01:04:09.700 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: No, I don't either.

01:04:09.700 --> 01:04:15.180 align:middle line:84%
ZEUS: I see it as the opening
to the kind of simplicity,

01:04:15.180 --> 01:04:18.560 align:middle line:84%
community action
and interaction.

01:04:18.560 --> 01:04:20.040 align:middle line:90%
Tiny homes is a great example.

01:04:20.040 --> 01:04:21.830 align:middle line:84%
What are the quality
of life things

01:04:21.830 --> 01:04:24.800 align:middle line:84%
that are brought in by
a tiny home, intimacy

01:04:24.800 --> 01:04:25.650 align:middle line:90%
being one of them?

01:04:25.650 --> 01:04:26.660 align:middle line:84%
You know, in the
old system, oh, I

01:04:26.660 --> 01:04:28.010 align:middle line:90%
want to stay away from somebody.

01:04:28.010 --> 01:04:29.510 align:middle line:90%
I want my distance.

01:04:29.510 --> 01:04:32.890 align:middle line:84%
But these huge McMansions
are creating situations

01:04:32.890 --> 01:04:35.170 align:middle line:84%
where families don't
even know each other.

01:04:35.170 --> 01:04:37.930 align:middle line:84%
They're watching TV, and
they're doing things separately.

01:04:37.930 --> 01:04:40.530 align:middle line:84%
With these tiny
homes, you're actively

01:04:40.530 --> 01:04:42.320 align:middle line:90%
participating together.

01:04:42.320 --> 01:04:45.400 align:middle line:90%
You're making meals together.

01:04:45.400 --> 01:04:50.420 align:middle line:84%
You have to fold the table
up to get your bed out,

01:04:50.420 --> 01:04:52.170 align:middle line:90%
or whatever it happens to be.

01:04:52.170 --> 01:04:55.490 align:middle line:84%
And as we begin to
understand that this

01:04:55.490 --> 01:05:00.240 align:middle line:84%
is where real quality of lies
in connection, in sharing

01:05:00.240 --> 01:05:03.270 align:middle line:84%
and giving, and also giving
to future generations,

01:05:03.270 --> 01:05:06.520 align:middle line:84%
tiny homes are making
the expense and footprint

01:05:06.520 --> 01:05:08.870 align:middle line:84%
that we have for future
generations much less.

01:05:08.870 --> 01:05:12.470 align:middle line:84%
So we're loving and sharing
people that haven't even

01:05:12.470 --> 01:05:13.940 align:middle line:90%
been born yet.

01:05:13.940 --> 01:05:16.630 align:middle line:84%
And this awakens
something in us.

01:05:16.630 --> 01:05:18.450 align:middle line:84%
You say, you're
buying back our soul.

01:05:18.450 --> 01:05:20.990 align:middle line:10%
This is awakening the spirit.

01:05:20.990 --> 01:05:22.990 align:middle line:10%
It's awakening the soul.

01:05:22.990 --> 01:05:28.320 align:middle line:10%
It's showing by your activities
in the world that you get it,

01:05:28.320 --> 01:05:29.710 align:middle line:10%
that it's about spirit.

01:05:29.710 --> 01:05:32.590 align:middle line:84%
It's about extending that
spirit to other people

01:05:32.590 --> 01:05:34.890 align:middle line:84%
and about doing it in these
really inventive ways,

01:05:34.890 --> 01:05:38.390 align:middle line:84%
like these tiny homes or
local currency or farmers

01:05:38.390 --> 01:05:40.320 align:middle line:90%
markets or urban gardening.

01:05:40.320 --> 01:05:41.120 align:middle line:90%
Oh, my gosh--

01:05:41.120 --> 01:05:42.203 align:middle line:90%
REGINA: All stuff we love.

01:05:42.203 --> 01:05:45.650 align:middle line:84%
ZEUS: Yes, exactly, we love
doing this, so let's do it.

01:05:45.650 --> 01:05:48.360 align:middle line:84%
REGINA: We need to assess
what our own true values are

01:05:48.360 --> 01:05:51.090 align:middle line:84%
and look at where we can
start conserving and buy back

01:05:51.090 --> 01:05:52.064 align:middle line:90%
our souls.

01:05:52.064 --> 01:05:52.980 align:middle line:90%
ZEUS: Oh, I love that.

01:05:52.980 --> 01:05:53.920 align:middle line:90%
I love that.

01:05:53.920 --> 01:05:55.012 align:middle line:90%
Buy back our souls.

01:05:55.012 --> 01:05:56.700 align:middle line:84%
REGINA: Yeah, buy back
our souls, meanwhile we'll

01:05:56.700 --> 01:05:58.200 align:middle line:84%
have you on for
another conversation

01:05:58.200 --> 01:06:01.060 align:middle line:84%
down the road on education
because your thoughts on it

01:06:01.060 --> 01:06:04.140 align:middle line:84%
are as clear and lucid
and as transformative,

01:06:04.140 --> 01:06:08.270 align:middle line:84%
destructive of the old system,
as your thoughts on this.

01:06:08.270 --> 01:06:11.890 align:middle line:84%
So again, I thank you
for your clear thinking.

